imary-color)\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 900;\">非对称压制</text>\r\n        <defs>\r\n          <marker id=\"redArrow\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"var(--primary-color)\"/></marker>\r\n        </defs>\r\n      </svg>\n</div>"
